data.description: Spotless four bedroom home in Oakbrook conveniently located just minutes from shopping and dining. Open layout with new luxury vinyl floors and split plan bedrooms. Enjoy greatly reduced electric bills with grid-tied solar panels. Oversized kitchen offers plenty of room for friends and family to gather and features 42 inch wood cabinetry, upgraded appliances and stainless steel farmhouse sink. Breakfast bar and formal dining room are perfect for entertaining. Primary suite features calming neutral color palette, double sinks and generous closet space. Unwind on the screened covered patio with peaceful lake views. Exterior features include fully fenced back yard, hurricane shutters, paver driveway and concrete block construction.
